# 7. Data Extraction Method

The paper does not explicitly define a formal data extraction protocol.

However, the study extracts and organizes information related to:

- software engineering practices
- TinyML engineering challenges
- proposed solutions
- workflow steps in TinyML engineering

The extracted information is summarized in structured tables.

Typical extracted fields include:

- TinyML workflow stage
- engineering challenge
- proposed solution
- origin of the solution (RQ1 or RQ2)

